{"TopicId":208896,"ForumId":51,"TopicTitle":"The Salamondastron Program: How to Reach the Speed of Light Without Cheats","CreatedByName":"Akagi","CreatedById":218751,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-07-08T18:42:19Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Akagi","CreatedById":218751,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-07-08T18:42:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022d6Ur2hf.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002264.00\u0022 height=\u0022674\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/d6Ur2hf.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNice afternoon for a launch.\u00A0\u003Cem\u003ESalamondastron 1\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0rockets upward, going where no rocket has gone before... of this class because it\u0027s a redesign of the original Salamonastrons.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022SvHNe6p.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002264.00\u0022 height=\u0022674\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/SvHNe6p.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAfter some worrying about the boosters and their decouplers almost overheating, I can detach the fairing, the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Launch Escape System\u0022\u003ELES\u003C/abbr\u003E, and the boosters.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022fqC6lIQ.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002264.00\u0022 height=\u0022674\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/fqC6lIQ.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFloating serenely in space. This is our first launch of the Salamondastron Program. Its goal? Reach the speed of light without cheats.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022a5XRKsS.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002264.00\u0022 height=\u0022674\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/a5XRKsS.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOrbital insertion burn. The Kerbals are very calm.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u002221LqEnR.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002264.00\u0022 height=\u0022674\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/21LqEnR.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDetaching the capsule. Testing the upper stage will be done another time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022mj8dZOm.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002264.00\u0022 height=\u0022674\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/mj8dZOm.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAfter warping to sunrise, we get this beautiful view of the capsule and the booster.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022HmxSDpK.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002264.00\u0022 height=\u0022674\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/HmxSDpK.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022iHORVBB.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002264.00\u0022 height=\u0022674\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/iHORVBB.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAssorted tests on the capsule\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022bwziudz.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002264.00\u0022 height=\u0022674\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/bwziudz.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is where we must end for now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ECURRENT STATS\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMax. Speed Reached: 1,811 m/s = a little fast\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOverall Distance Flown: 26,581 m = not far\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nShips Launched: 1 = not many at all\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vagrant203","CreatedById":202630,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-07-08T23:16:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224153035\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022208896\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221657305739\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022218751\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Akagi\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, Akagi said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSalamondastron\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAny relation to the mountain Salamandastron from the Redwall series?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Akagi","CreatedById":218751,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-07-08T23:34:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224153104\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022208896\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221657322214\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022202630\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vagrant203\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 minutes ago, Vagrant203 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAny relation to the mountain Salamandastron from the Redwall series?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAll relation.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}